ormed a few Myrs ago, and the cloud\ndispersal by the O stars is significant. We conclude that cloud-cloud collision\noffers a possible explanation of the min-starburst over a 100-pc scale.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Jun 2017 03:31:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 Jun 2017 07:53:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 26 Jun 2017 13:10:34 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 27 Jun 2017 09:04:13 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 25 Jan 2018 05:11:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-11"}
