ackground in dark matter experiments, requiring the application of\nspecific protocols for target material purification, material storing\nunderground and limiting the time the detector is on surface during the\nbuilding process in order to minimize the exposure to the most dangerous cosmic\nray components.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 19 Jun 2017 08:04:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Nov 2017 10:45:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-06"}
